ClassicComplementInterface, DeterministicComplementInterface, KurshanComplementInterface, ModifiedSafraComplementInterface, MullerSchuppComplementInterface, PitermanComplementInterface, RamseyComplementInterface, RankComplementInterface, SafraComplementInterface, SliceComplementInterface, WAAComplementInterface, WAPAComplementInterface
public abstract class AbstractComplementConstructionInterface
extends java.lang.Object
implements ComplementConstructionInterface

This class provides a default implementation of ComplementConstructionInterface. The initial value of command name is an empty string, the initial value of the construction class is null, and the initial value of the help message is an empty string.

Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
